    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Ghost Frequency | 幽灵频率》</strong>是一款第一人称恐怖游戏，你将扮演马克，一位来自<strong>PIT - 超自然现象调查组</strong>的资深捉鬼大师。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d0fe9f4b67e636921dcdaf2d0d0e7599.poster.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d0fe9f4b67e636921dcdaf2d0d0e7599.webm?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d0fe9f4b67e636921dcdaf2d0d0e7599.mp4?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你与你的搭档艾米丽一同踏入被诅咒的废弃领域，寻找你失踪的朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你一踏入这里就发现空气中弥漫着不祥的气息，仿佛每一片阴影都隐藏着不可名状的恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/ff006df4fbe5fc44fb213431e8b14112.poster.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/ff006df4fbe5fc44fb213431e8b14112.webm?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/ff006df4fbe5fc44fb213431e8b14112.mp4?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为资深捉鬼大师，工具当然必不可少:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EMF电磁探测器</strong>: 通过检测电磁频率追踪超自然现象，揭示隐藏的实体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d076ce443c6ec6154485bbce07cb68a5.poster.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d076ce443c6ec6154485bbce07cb68a5.webm?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/d076ce443c6ec6154485bbce07cb68a5.mp4?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>红外热像仪</strong>: 超越人类视界的极限，捕捉那些肉眼无法察觉的异象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/0699f816999a636814b29d7a7dce9ee5.poster.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/0699f816999a636814b29d7a7dce9ee5.webm?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/0699f816999a636814b29d7a7dce9ee5.mp4?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EVP数字录音机</strong>:在寂静的夜晚，它将成为你倾听异界的耳朵，它就专为录制这些的声音而设计的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/35c51b74ef729bb2fa092b18c8852e62.poster.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/35c51b74ef729bb2fa092b18c8852e62.webm?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/35c51b74ef729bb2fa092b18c8852e62.mp4?t=1752684340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PIT - 超自然现象调查队</strong>是意大利著名的捉鬼团队，他们根据亲身的冒险经历开发出了<strong>Ghost Finder Tools</strong>软件，这款终极捉鬼工具已逾一百万人下载，在170个国家投入使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/809f925a30687e495e247da39ddb7ea2.avif?t=1752684340\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，是否拥有勇气，成为下一个调查队的传奇？</p>",
